oofem.out
Reinforced plate (rebar via #@rebar directive)
NonLinearStatic nmsteps 1 nsteps 1 profileopt 1 nmodules 1 contextOutputStep 1000
nsteps 1 rtolf 1.e-3 stiffMode 0 maxiter 1000 controllmode 1 donotfixload
vtkxmllattice primvars 1 1 cellvars 4 46 60 90 111 tstep_all domain_all cross 1
domain 3d
OutputManager tstep_step 1 dofman_output { 1 }
ncrosssect 2 nmat 2 nbc 1 nic 0 nltf 2 nset 1
LatticeCS 1 material 1 shape 2
LatticeCS 2 material 2 shape 1 radius 0.006
LatticeFrameElastic 1 d 1. tAlpha 0.0 E 30.e9 n 0.0
LatticeFrameSteelPlastic 2 d 1. tAlpha 0.0 E 200.e9 n 0.0 talpha 0
#@INSERT_LIVELOADS
ConstantFunction 1 f(t) 1.0
PiecewiseLinFunction 2 t 2 0 1 f(t) 2 1 1.
#@INSERT_SETS
#@LOAD patch 1 q 0.
#@DIR 0 0 -1
#@THICKNESS 0.01
#@SHELLWIDTHSCALE 1.

#@BC vertex 1 dofs 3 1 2 3 values 3 0 0 0

#@rebar 5 diameter 0.012 crossSect 2 mat 2 bondCS 1 bondMat 1

#@mesher t3d
